# Secrets — never sweep local env/key material into the Cloud Build source bucket.
# gcloud uses .gcloudignore EXCLUSIVELY when present and does NOT fall back to
# .gitignore, so `.env` being gitignored is not enough. See SECURITY_AUDIT_2026-06
# (INFRA-1): `gcloud builds submit .` would otherwise upload any local secret
# (Supabase service-role key, relayer/owner PRIVATE_KEY, Firebase Admin SA JSON)
# to gs://<project>_cloudbuild.
.env
*.env
.env.*
**/.env
frontend/.env
*.pem
*.key
# Service-account / credential JSON (GCIP import + Firebase deploy).
*-admin.json
service-account*.json
serviceAccount*.json
*-sa.json
firebase-debug.log
.firebase/
firebase*.generated.json
firebase.*.generated.json
